Arnold 4.1 Renderer Info Dump Utility
=====================================

Environment Variables
---------------------

ARNOLDTREE_4_1  The installation directory of Arnold 4.1
KATANA_HOME     The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/ArnoldRendererInfoDump' to the 'RenderBin' subdirectory
   within a Katana resources path.
